DGAP Post-admission Duties announcement: Zalando SE / Disclosure according to Art. 5 para. 1 lit. b) and para. 3 Regulation (EU) No. 596/2014 and Art. 2 para. 3 Commission Delegated Regulation (EU) No. 2016/1052 // Share buy-back - 1st interim reporting
Zalando SE: Release of a capital market information 

23.03.2018 / 19:22 
